            "text": "A short energy statement for the end of Week 2 of the MONEY program. The old story ran for generations; the new one is already in motion. This statement names both.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to energy statements? Read ",
